This paper is about improving the performance of a neural named entity recognition system, which is a task in natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques for generating gazetteers, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves database techniques for integrating the gazetteers into the NER system, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases).
